{
  "chapter": 30,
  "chapter_summary": "第三十回「一不做二不休」：连城璧突施杀手，先杀何平、郑刚灭口，随即将割鹿刀归还萧十一郎，表明自己已改变主意。他道出入天宗是为了毁灭这个组织，为无垢山庄三百年清誉而忍辱负重。众人饮酒交谈，连城璧坦言自己也尝过真正的痛苦，因而能理解萧十一郎。他透露天宗组织严密，却连宗主真面目也未曾见过。月圆之夜，养着狗的天宗宗主乘舟而来，却远远停下，三条小船同时围拢过来。风四娘心中疑云密布——冰冰安排的西湖之行，莫非是泄露萧十一郎行踪的关键？",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_lian_cheng_bi",
      "speaker_name": "连城璧",
      "listener": "char_he_ping",
      "text": "何平兄，请过来说话。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 8,
      "line_end": 8
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_he_ping",
      "speaker_name": "何平",
      "listener": "char_lian_cheng_bi",
      "text": "公子有何吩咐？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 10,
      "line_end": 10
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lian_cheng_bi",
      "speaker_name": "连城璧",
      "listener": "char_he_ping",
      "text": "我只不过想请教一件事。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 12,
      "line_end": 12
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_he_ping",
      "speaker_name": "何平",
      "listener": "char_lian_cheng_bi",
      "text": "不敢。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 14,
      "line_end": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lian_cheng_bi",
      "speaker_name": "连城璧",
      "listener": "char_he_ping",
      "text": "你知不知道我为什么要杀花如玉？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 16,
      "line_end": 16
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lian_cheng_bi",
      "speaker_name": "连城璧",
      "listener": "char_he_ping",
      "text": "你真的不知道？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 22,
      "line_end": 22
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_he_ping",
      "speaker_name": "何平",
      "listener": "char_lian_cheng_bi",
      "text": "真的不知道。",
      "tone": "慌张",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 24,
      "line_end": 24
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lian_cheng_bi",
      "speaker_name": "连城璧",
      "listener": "char_he_ping",
      "text": "连这种事都不知道，你这人活着还有什么意思？",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 26,
      "line_end": 26
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lian_cheng_bi",
      "speaker_name": "连城璧",
      "listener": "char_zheng_gang",
      "text": "郑刚兄，我也有件事想请教。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 36,
      "line_end": 36
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zheng_gang",
      "speaker_name": "郑刚",
      "listener": "char_lian_cheng_bi",
      "text": "你说，我听得见。",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 40,
      "line_end": 40
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zheng_gang",
      "speaker_name": "郑刚",
      "listener": "char_lian_cheng_bi",
      "text": "我跟姓花的素无来往，你就是再砍他十刀，我也不会多说一句话。",
      "tone": "慌张",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 42,
      "line_end": 42
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lian_cheng_bi",
      "speaker_name": "连城璧",
      "listener": "char_zheng_gang",
      "text": "我只不过问你，你知不知道我为什么要杀他？",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 46,
      "line_end": 46
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lian_cheng_bi",
      "speaker_name": "连城璧",
      "listener": "char_zheng_gang",
      "text": "你知道我是为了什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 50,
      "line_end": 50
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zheng_gang",
      "speaker_name": "郑刚",
      "listener": "char_lian_cheng_bi",
      "text": "我们本是来杀萧十一郎的，可是你却忽然改变了主意。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 52,
      "line_end": 52
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lian_cheng_bi",
      "speaker_name": "连城璧",
      "listener": "char_zheng_gang",
      "text": "说下去！",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 54,
      "line_end": 54
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zheng_gang",
      "speaker_name": "郑刚",
      "listener": "char_lian_cheng_bi",
      "text": "临阵变节，本是'天宗'大忌，你怕他泄露这秘密，就索性杀了他灭口。",
      "tone": "颤声",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 56,
      "line_end": 56
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lian_cheng_bi",
      "speaker_name": "连城璧",
      "listener": "char_zheng_gang",
      "text": "你连这种事都知道，我怎么能让你活下去？",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 60,
      "line_end": 60
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lian_cheng_bi",
      "speaker_name": "连城璧",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "果然是天下无双的利器，果然名下无虚。",
      "tone": "喃喃",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 70,
      "line_end": 70
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": "char_lian_cheng_bi",
      "text": "一别经年，你的出手好像一点也没有慢。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 76,
      "line_end": 76
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lian_cheng_bi",
      "speaker_name": "连城璧",
      "listener": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "text": "这把刀也没有钝。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 78,
      "line_end": 78
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": "char_lian_cheng_bi",
      "text": "我只知道你的剑法很高，想不到你也会用刀。",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 80,
      "line_end": 80
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lian_cheng_bi",
      "speaker_name": "连城璧",
      "listener": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "text": "刀剑都是杀人的利器，我会杀人。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 82,
      "line_end": 82
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": "char_lian_cheng_bi",
      "text": "会用刀的人，若是有了这么样一把刀，肯不肯再还给别人？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 84,
      "line_end": 85
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lian_cheng_bi",
      "speaker_name": "连城璧",
      "listener": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "text": "不肯。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 88,
      "line_end": 88
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lian_cheng_bi",
      "speaker_name": "连城璧",
      "listener": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "text": "我也绝不肯将这把刀还给别人，我只肯还给他。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 94,
      "line_end": 94
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": "char_lian_cheng_bi",
      "text": "为什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 96,
      "line_end": 96
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lian_cheng_bi",
      "speaker_name": "连城璧",
      "listener": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "text": "因为他是萧十一郎。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 98,
      "line_end": 98
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": "char_lian_cheng_bi",
      "text": "只有萧十一郎才配用这把刀？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 100,
      "line_end": 100
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": "char_lian_cheng_bi",
      "text": "这把刀若不是刀，而是剑呢？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 106,
      "line_end": 106
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lian_cheng_bi",
      "speaker_name": "连城璧",
      "listener": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "text": "这把刀若是剑，这柄剑就是我的。",
      "tone": "自信",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 108,
      "line_end": 108
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": "char_lian_cheng_bi",
      "text": "看来你的人也没有变。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 116,
      "line_end": 116
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": "char_lian_cheng_bi",
      "text": "有些人就像是这把刀一样，这把刀永不会钝，这种人也永不会变。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 118,
      "line_end": 118
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": "char_lian_cheng_bi",
      "text": "我记得你以前也喝酒的？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 120,
      "line_end": 121
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lian_cheng_bi",
      "speaker_name": "连城璧",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "你没有记错。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 124,
      "line_end": 124
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": "char_lian_cheng_bi",
      "text": "现在呢？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 126,
      "line_end": 126
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lian_cheng_bi",
      "speaker_name": "连城璧",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "你说过，有种人是永远不变的，喝酒的人就通常都是这种人。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 128,
      "line_end": 128
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": "char_lian_cheng_bi",
      "text": "你是不是这种人？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 132,
      "line_end": 132
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lian_cheng_bi",
      "speaker_name": "连城璧",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "是。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 134,
      "line_end": 134
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": "char_lian_cheng_bi",
      "text": "你本来真的是要来杀我们的？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 150,
      "line_end": 150
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lian_cheng_bi",
      "speaker_name": "连城璧",
      "listener": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "text": "这本是个很周密的计划，我们已计划了很久。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 152,
      "line_end": 152
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": "char_lian_cheng_bi",
      "text": "可是你却忽然改变了主意。",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 154,
      "line_end": 154
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lian_cheng_bi",
      "speaker_name": "连城璧",
      "listener": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "text": "我的人虽然不会变，主意却常常会变。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 156,
      "line_end": 156
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": "char_lian_cheng_bi",
      "text": "这次你为什么会变？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 158,
      "line_end": 158
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lian_cheng_bi",
      "speaker_name": "连城璧",
      "listener": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "text": "因为我听见了你们刚才在这里说的话。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 160,
      "line_end": 160
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": "char_lian_cheng_bi",
      "text": "你全都听见了。",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 162,
      "line_end": 162
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lian_cheng_bi",
      "speaker_name": "连城璧",
      "listener": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "text": "我听得很清楚，所以我才能了解他是个什么样的人。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 164,
      "line_end": 164
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": "char_lian_cheng_bi",
      "text": "你真的已了解？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 166,
      "line_end": 166
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lian_cheng_bi",
      "speaker_name": "连城璧",
      "listener": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "text": "至少我已明白，他并不是别人想像中那种冷酷无情的人，他虽然毁了我们，可是他心里却可能比我们更痛苦。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 168,
      "line_end": 168
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": "char_lian_cheng_bi",
      "text": "只可惜他的痛苦从来也没有人了解，更没有人同情。",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 172,
      "line_end": 172
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lian_cheng_bi",
      "speaker_name": "连城璧",
      "listener": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "text": "快乐虽有很多种，真正的痛苦，却是同样的，你若也尝受过真正的痛苦，就一定能了解别人的痛苦。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 176,
      "line_end": 176
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": "char_lian_cheng_bi",
      "text": "也只有真正尝过痛苦滋味的人，才能了解别人的痛苦。",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 180,
      "line_end": 180
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lian_cheng_bi",
      "speaker_name": "连城璧",
      "listener": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "text": "我了解，我很久以前就已了解……",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 184,
      "line_end": 184
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lian_cheng_bi",
      "speaker_name": "连城璧",
      "listener": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "text": "就因为我了解这种痛苦的可怕，所以才不愿看着大家再为这件事痛苦下去。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 192,
      "line_end": 192
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": "char_lian_cheng_bi",
      "text": "真的？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 196,
      "line_end": 196
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lian_cheng_bi",
      "speaker_name": "连城璧",
      "listener": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "text": "该走的，迟早总是要走了，现在她已走了，已去到她自己想去的地方，也已将所有的恩怨仇恨都带走了，这既然是她的意思，我们为什么不能把心里的仇恨忘记？",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 200,
      "line_end": 200
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": "char_lian_cheng_bi",
      "text": "不错，她的确已将所有的仇恨带走了，我现在才明白她的意思，我一直都误会了她。",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 204,
      "line_end": 204
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lian_cheng_bi",
      "speaker_name": "连城璧",
      "listener": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "text": "该走的已走了，该结束的也已将结束，我又何必再制造新的仇恨？",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 212,
      "line_end": 212
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": "char_lian_cheng_bi",
      "text": "所以你才会改变了主意？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 216,
      "line_end": 216
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lian_cheng_bi",
      "speaker_name": "连城璧",
      "listener": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "text": "何况我也知道每个人都难免会做错事的，一个人若能为自己做错了的事而痛苦，岂非就已等于付出了代价。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 218,
      "line_end": 218
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": "char_lian_cheng_bi",
      "text": "你也做错过事？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 226,
      "line_end": 226
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lian_cheng_bi",
      "speaker_name": "连城璧",
      "listener": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "text": "我也是人。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 228,
      "line_end": 228
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": "char_lian_cheng_bi",
      "text": "你也已知道你本不该投入'天宗'的？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 230,
      "line_end": 230
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lian_cheng_bi",
      "speaker_name": "连城璧",
      "listener": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "text": "这件事我并没有错。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 232,
      "line_end": 232
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": "char_lian_cheng_bi",
      "text": "没错？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 234,
      "line_end": 234
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lian_cheng_bi",
      "speaker_name": "连城璧",
      "listener": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "text": "我入天宗，只有一个目的。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 236,
      "line_end": 236
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": "char_lian_cheng_bi",
      "text": "什么目的？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 238,
      "line_end": 238
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lian_cheng_bi",
      "speaker_name": "连城璧",
      "listener": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "text": "揭发他们的阴谋，彻底毁灭他们的组织。",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 240,
      "line_end": 240
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lian_cheng_bi",
      "speaker_name": "连城璧",
      "listener": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "text": "我故意装作消沉落魄，并不是为了要骗你们，你现在想必已明白我为的是什么？",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 242,
      "line_end": 242
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": "char_lian_cheng_bi",
      "text": "我一点也不明白。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 246,
      "line_end": 246
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lian_cheng_bi",
      "speaker_name": "连城璧",
      "listener": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "text": "你知不知道连城璧是什么样的人？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 248,
      "line_end": 248
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": "char_lian_cheng_bi",
      "text": "是个很冷静，很精明，也很自负的人。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 250,
      "line_end": 250
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lian_cheng_bi",
      "speaker_name": "连城璧",
      "listener": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "text": "像这么样一个人，若是突然要投入天宗，你会怎么想？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 254,
      "line_end": 254
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": "char_lian_cheng_bi",
      "text": "我会想他一定别有用心。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 258,
      "line_end": 258
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lian_cheng_bi",
      "speaker_name": "连城璧",
      "listener": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "text": "所以你若是天宗的宗主，就算让他入了天宗，也一样会对他格外提防的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 260,
      "line_end": 260
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": "char_lian_cheng_bi",
      "text": "不错。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 264,
      "line_end": 264
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lian_cheng_bi",
      "speaker_name": "连城璧",
      "listener": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "text": "可是一个消沉落魄的酒鬼，就不同了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 266,
      "line_end": 266
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": "char_lian_cheng_bi",
      "text": "但我却还是不懂，你为什么要对付天宗？为什么要如此委屈自己？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 268,
      "line_end": 270
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lian_cheng_bi",
      "speaker_name": "连城璧",
      "listener": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "text": "自从我的远祖云村公赤手空拳，创建了无垢山庄，到如今已三百年，这三百年来，无垢山庄的子弟，无论在何时何地，都同样受人尊敬。",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 272,
      "line_end": 272
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lian_cheng_bi",
      "speaker_name": "连城璧",
      "listener": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "text": "我的玄祖天峰公，为了替江湖武林同盟争一点公道，独上天山，找当时威镇天下的天山七剑恶战三昼夜，负伤二十九处，却终于还是逼着天山七剑同下江南，负荆请罪。",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 278,
      "line_end": 278
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lian_cheng_bi",
      "speaker_name": "连城璧",
      "listener": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "text": "五十年前，魔教南侵，与江南水霸勾结，组成七十二帮黑道联盟，先祖父奋袂而起，身经大小八十战，战无不胜，江南武林才总算没有遭受到他们的荼毒，有很多人家至今还供着他老人家的长生禄位。",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 280,
      "line_end": 280
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lian_cheng_bi",
      "speaker_name": "连城璧",
      "listener": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "text": "我也是连家的子孙，我绝不能让无垢山庄的威名毁在我手上，也绝不能眼看着天宗的阴谋得逞。",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 288,
      "line_end": 288
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": "char_lian_cheng_bi",
      "text": "就凭这句话，我已该敬你三杯。",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 292,
      "line_end": 292
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lian_cheng_bi",
      "speaker_name": "连城璧",
      "listener": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "text": "只可惜直到现在，我还不知道天宗的宗主究竟是谁？",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 294,
      "line_end": 294
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": "char_lian_cheng_bi",
      "text": "你还不知道？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 298,
      "line_end": 298
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": "char_lian_cheng_bi",
      "text": "难道他在你面前，也从来没有露出过真面目？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 302,
      "line_end": 302
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": "char_lian_cheng_bi",
      "text": "难道他还不信任你？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 306,
      "line_end": 306
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lian_cheng_bi",
      "speaker_name": "连城璧",
      "listener": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "text": "他从来也没有信任过任何人，这世上惟一能见到他真面目的，也许只有他养的那条狗了。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 308,
      "line_end": 308
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lian_cheng_bi",
      "speaker_name": "连城璧",
      "listener": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "text": "我就知道他一定会来的。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 316,
      "line_end": 316
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": "char_lian_cheng_bi",
      "text": "他虽然养了条狗，养狗的人却未必一定就是他。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 318,
      "line_end": 318
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lian_cheng_bi",
      "speaker_name": "连城璧",
      "listener": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "text": "一定是他。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 320,
      "line_end": 320
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": "char_lian_cheng_bi",
      "text": "你们约的岂非是月圆之夜？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 322,
      "line_end": 322
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lian_cheng_bi",
      "speaker_name": "连城璧",
      "listener": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "text": "今夜的月就已圆了。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 324,
      "line_end": 324
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": "char_lian_cheng_bi",
      "text": "他知道你在这里？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 330,
      "line_end": 330
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lian_cheng_bi",
      "speaker_name": "连城璧",
      "listener": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "text": "但他却不知道我已改变了主意。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 332,
      "line_end": 332
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": "char_lian_cheng_bi",
      "text": "现在他一定以为萧十一郎已死在你手里。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 334,
      "line_end": 334
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lian_cheng_bi",
      "speaker_name": "连城璧",
      "listener": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "text": "所以他一定要来看看。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 336,
      "line_end": 336
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": "char_lian_cheng_bi",
      "text": "看什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 338,
      "line_end": 338
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lian_cheng_bi",
      "speaker_name": "连城璧",
      "listener": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "text": "看萧十一郎的人头。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 340,
      "line_end": 340
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": "char_lian_cheng_bi",
      "text": "难道他一定要亲眼看见萧十一郎的人头落地？",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 342,
      "line_end": 342
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lian_cheng_bi",
      "speaker_name": "连城璧",
      "listener": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "text": "他自己也说过，只要萧十一郎还活着，他就食不知味，寝难安枕。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 344,
      "line_end": 344
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": "char_lian_cheng_bi",
      "text": "这件事你们已计划了多久？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 348,
      "line_end": 348
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lian_cheng_bi",
      "speaker_name": "连城璧",
      "listener": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "text": "已有半个月了。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 350,
      "line_end": 350
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": "char_lian_cheng_bi",
      "text": "半个月前，你们怎么知道萧十一郎会到这水月楼来？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 352,
      "line_end": 352
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lian_cheng_bi",
      "speaker_name": "连城璧",
      "listener": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "text": "无论谁身边，都难免有人会走漏消息，将他的行迹泄露出来。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 354,
      "line_end": 354
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": "char_lian_cheng_bi",
      "text": "你认为是谁泄露了他的行踪？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 358,
      "line_end": 358
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lian_cheng_bi",
      "speaker_name": "连城璧",
      "listener": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "text": "不知道。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 360,
      "line_end": 360
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": "char_lian_cheng_bi",
      "text": "半个月之前，也许连萧十一郎都不知道他会到水月楼来。",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 362,
      "line_end": 362
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lian_cheng_bi",
      "speaker_name": "连城璧",
      "listener": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "text": "一定有个人知道的，否则我们又怎会把约会订在这里？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 366,
      "line_end": 366
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lian_cheng_bi",
      "speaker_name": "连城璧",
      "listener": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "text": "天宗组织之严密，天下无双，可是天宗里却也难免有叛徒存在。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 384,
      "line_end": 384
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": "char_lian_cheng_bi",
      "text": "你知道那些叛徒是些什么人？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 388,
      "line_end": 388
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lian_cheng_bi",
      "speaker_name": "连城璧",
      "listener": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "text": "都是些死人。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 390,
      "line_end": 390
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": "char_lian_cheng_bi",
      "text": "死人？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 392,
      "line_end": 392
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lian_cheng_bi",
      "speaker_name": "连城璧",
      "listener": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "text": "据我所知，天宗的叛徒，现在几乎都已死得干干净净。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 394,
      "line_end": 394
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": "char_lian_cheng_bi",
      "text": "是谁杀了他们？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 398,
      "line_end": 398
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lian_cheng_bi",
      "speaker_name": "连城璧",
      "listener": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "text": "萧十一郎！",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 400,
      "line_end": 400
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lian_cheng_bi",
      "speaker_name": "连城璧",
      "listener": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "text": "所以你只要多看他两眼，你的眼睛就会花了。",
      "tone": "低语",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 420,
      "line_end": 420
    }
  ],
